774
00:40:04,398 --> 00:40:08,133
And what if we could
harness it in some way?

775
00:40:10,515 --> 00:40:13,867
This is an office block
in the centre of London.

776
00:40:14,078 --> 00:40:17,484
Like many office blocks,
it has a revolving door,

777
00:40:17,750 --> 00:40:21,937
