00:41:01,500 --> 00:41:03,261
I'm charging my phone,

792
00:41:03,461 --> 00:41:05,023
So, dog's harnessed.

793
00:41:05,164 --> 00:41:06,932
That was easy.
Attached to the trailer.

794
00:41:07,008 --> 00:41:09,367
All I've got to do
is set her going.

795
00:41:09,726 --> 00:41:12,367
And I've even planned
