Catch him! Chop-chop!

815
00:42:21,875 --> 00:42:24,743
This is the work of a genius.

816
00:42:24,984 --> 00:42:26,277
Back in the countryside,

817
00:42:26,406 --> 00:42:27,846
I'd mended my dog

818
00:42:27,913 --> 00:42:30,523
